---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="HVAC Services in Cedar Creek, TX | String Prairie Heating & Air"
	description="Local heating and air conditioning services in Cedar Creek, Texas. Family-owned HVAC company providing installation, repair, and maintenance in Cedar Creek and surrounding Bastrop County."
>
	<section class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>HVAC Services in Cedar Creek, TX</h1>
			<p>Your local heating and air conditioning experts</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="area-content">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="area-intro">
				<h2>Serving Cedar Creek with Expert HVAC Services</h2>
				<p class="lead">
					Cedar Creek is a growing community in Bastrop County, and String Prairie Heating & Air is proud to serve its residents with professional heating and cooling services. From the established neighborhoods to the newer developments along Highway 71, we understand the unique HVAC needs of Cedar Creek homes and are committed to keeping families comfortable year-round.
				</p>
				<p class="lead">
					Whether you need a new system installed in your dream home, emergency repairs during a scorching Texas summer, or regular maintenance to keep your HVAC running efficiently, our experienced technicians are ready to help. Our central location in the Rosanky area means fast response times for Cedar Creek customers.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="areas-served">
				<h3>Areas We Serve in Cedar Creek</h3>
				<p>
					We provide HVAC services throughout the Cedar Creek community including properties along Highway 71, homes in Cedar Creek subdivisions, ranches and rural properties in the Cedar Creek area, homes near FM 535, and all surrounding developments. Our local presence in Bastrop County means we can respond quickly to your heating and cooling needs.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="services-overview">
				<h2>Complete HVAC Services for Cedar Creek Homes & Businesses</h2>
				<div class="services-list">
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Air Conditioning</h3>
						<p>AC installation, repair, maintenance, and emergency service to keep you cool during hot Texas summers.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Heating Systems</h3>
						<p>Furnace and heat pump installation, repair, and maintenance for comfortable winters.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Maintenance Plans</h3>
						<p>Preventive maintenance to extend system life, improve efficiency, and prevent breakdowns.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Emergency Service</h3>
						<p>Fast response when you need it most - we understand HVAC emergencies can't wait.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="local-advantages">
				<h2>Why Cedar Creek Residents Choose String Prairie</h2>
				<ul class="advantage-list">
					<li>Family-owned and operated - we're part of your community</li>
					<li>Fast local response times for emergencies</li>
					<li>Experience with both new construction and existing homes</li>
					<li>Honest, transparent pricing with no hidden fees</li>
					<li>Fully licensed and insured for your protection</li>
					<li>Expert knowledge of Central Texas climate challenges</li>
					<li>Quality workmanship backed by solid warranties</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="map-section">
				<h2>Find Us on the Map</h2>
				<p class="map-subtitle">Serving Cedar Creek and all of Bastrop County</p>
				<div class="map-container">
					<iframe
						src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d27593.68!2d-97.48!3d30.08!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x8644d3f9c4a4a4a5%3A0x9b9b9b9b9b9b9b9b!2sCedar%20Creek%2C%20TX!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1234567890"
						width="100%"
						height="450"
						style="border:0; border-radius: 12px;"
						allowfullscreen=""
						loading="lazy"
						referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
					</iframe>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="testimonials-section">
				<h2>What Cedar Creek Customers Say</h2>
				<p class="testimonials-subtitle">Hear from your neighbors about their experience with String Prairie Heating & Air</p>
				<div class="testimonials-grid">
					<div class="testimonial-card">
						<div class="stars">*****</div>
						<p class="testimonial-text">"We just moved to Cedar Creek and needed our AC serviced. String Prairie was recommended by a neighbor and I'm so glad we called! Professional, punctual, and reasonably priced."</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">- Jennifer L., Cedar Creek</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-card">
						<div class="stars">*****</div>
						<p class="testimonial-text">"String Prairie installed a new HVAC system in our Cedar Creek home. The team was incredibly professional and knowledgeable. They explained everything and made sure we were completely satisfied."</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">- Brian & Michelle R., Cedar Creek</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-card">
						<div class="stars">*****</div>
						<p class="testimonial-text">"Our AC died on the hottest day of summer. String Prairie came out the same day and had us back up and running by evening. Can't thank them enough for the fast service!"</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">- Carlos M., Cedar Creek</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="review-cta">
					<a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/String+Prairie+Heating+%26+Air/@29.8918229,-97.3320232" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="review-link">Leave us a Google Review</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="cta-section-local">
				<h2>Schedule Your HVAC Service in Cedar Creek</h2>
				<p>Ready for reliable HVAC service from your local experts? Contact us today!</p>
				<div class="cta-buttons">
					<a href="https://book.housecallpro.com/book/String-Prairie-Heating--Air/df82ded280ce43f4a9ee6ee6d36aef76?v2=true" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Book Online</a>
					<a href="tel:5129249744" class="btn btn-secondary">Call (512) 924-9744</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

