		padding: 5rem 0;
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

