		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-weight: 300;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.areas-served {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue) 0%, var(--dark-blue) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.areas-served h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.areas-served p {
